narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think we could have spent more time on each essay really deciphering each part.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would highly recommend this section of ENGL114 under Prof. Shoemaker. He provided clear feedback for every essay and always encouraged us to improve on our previous work. Class discussions were very engaging thanks to the smaller class size and every student was able to share their unique ideas of Time and the human experience of it. The class workload is spaced out throughout the semester and the final assignment is a shorter writing piece, so it was never too difficult.
Yes, a lot of very interesting topics about time were discussed.
